==游戏中的出现==
*A [[cover_version|cover version]] of the song appears in ''[[Elite_Beat_Agents|Elite Beat Agents]]''. In the stage, the player must cheer on a taxi driver as he races to the hospital for a pregnant woman entering [[Childbirth|labor]].
*''[[SingStar_Pop|SingStar Pop]]'' ([[PlayStation_2|PlayStation 2]] game)

